Google sheets via Gargle auth

raw <- readBin("keys/sheets.json", "raw", file.size("keys/sheets.json"))
pth <- sodium::data_decrypt(bin = raw,
                     key = sodium::sha256(charToRaw(Sys.getenv("UO_SHEETS_PASSWORD"))),
                     nonce = gargle:::secret_nonce())

googlesheets4::gs4_auth(email = "pbouchal@gmail.com", path = rawToChar(pth))
dns <- googlesheets4::read_sheet("1ohis0XYklKjIdhbdh1Ca_0qKy-etXQhw1EiEXFfBAdI",
                                 col_types = "c---------cciicccc") %>%
  rename(redizo = RED_IZO) %>%
  clean_names()

TODO: test BigQuery via Gargle auth

raw <- readBin("keys/bq.json", "raw", file.size("keys/bq.json"))
pth <- sodium::data_decrypt(bin = raw,
                     key = sodium::sha256(charToRaw(Sys.getenv("UO_BQ_PASSWORD"))),
                     nonce = gargle:::secret_nonce())

library(bigrquery)

bq_auth(email = "pbouchal@gmail.com", path = rawToChar(pth))

prjname <- "ucimeonline"
dsname <- "technologickamapa"
bqc <- dbConnect(
  bigrquery::bigquery(),
  project = prjname,
  dataset = dsname,
  billing = prjname
)
try(bigrquery::bq_table_delete(bq_table(prjname, dsname, "mtcars")))
bigrquery::bq_table_upload(bq_table("ucimeonline", "technologickamapa", "mtcars"),
                           values = mtcars)
tbl(bqc, "mtcars")
